highlights.text: “Fade Into You” by Mazzy Star is the biggest gainer on Top Songs Australia, up 45 spots at #146.
Sabrina Carpenter has the most spots on Top Songs Australia. “Tears” is the highest at #4.
“Mr. Brightside” by The Killers has been on Top Songs Australia the longest, at 2080 days straight.
“who’s your boyfriend” by Royel Otis is the highest new entry on Top Songs Australia at #142.
